OL,3,CFamily of father-of-three killed in
OL,4,Cstabbing says his 'legacy will live on'
OL,6,FThe family of a dad who was stabbed
OL,7,Fand killed has vowed to carry on his
OL,8,Flegacy.
OL,10,FAdrian Brown died in hospital after he
OL,11,Fwas attacked on Raby Street in Moss
OL,12,FSide, Manchester at around 11pm on
OL,13,FFriday 8 May.
OL,15,FAdrian's family described the father-
OL,16,Fof-three as a "loving son, brother,
OL,17,Funcle, boyfriend" who "adored being a
OL,18,Fdad".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
