OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778576786
OL,3,CFamily of father-of-three killed in
OL,4,Cstabbing says his 'legacy will live on'
OL,6,FPaying tribute, Adrian's partner and
OL,7,Fthe mother of his three children Tamia
OL,8,FZameer said: "R.I.P to my number one,
OL,9,FAdrian. I love you always and forever.
OL,10,FMe and your boys will cherish every
OL,11,Fmoment that we had.
OL,13,F"We will miss you so much. Your legacy
OL,14,Fwill forever live on and I will get
OL,15,Fthe justice that you deserve."
OL,17,FHis mother, Jennifer Meade, added: "My
OL,18,Fson, you did not deserve this. I can't
OL,19,Fput into words how I feel. They took
OL,20,Fmy boy.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
