OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778576786
OL,3,CFamily of father-of-three killed in
OL,4,Cstabbing says his 'legacy will live on'
OL,6,F"He was a loving son, brother, uncle,
OL,7,Fboyfriend, and he adored being a dad
OL,8,Fto my grandkids. I will miss you so
OL,9,Fmuch. Rest in peace, son. I love you
OL,10,Fmore than you know."
OL,12,FAdrian was found with stab wounds to
OL,13,Fthe chest and died of his injuries. An
OL,14,F18-year-old man was arrested on
OL,15,Fsuspicion of murder on Saturday 9 May
OL,16,Fand remains in custody.
OL,18,FA second man, aged 24, has also been
OL,19,Farrested on suspicion of murder.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
