PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778576786
OL,3,CFamily of father-of-three killed in
OL,4,Cstabbing says his 'legacy will live on'
OL,6,FTwo men, aged 25 and 38, and a 26-year-
OL,7,Fold woman have also been arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender.
OL,10,FDetective Chief Inspector Louise
OL,11,FEdwards, from the Major Incident Team,
OL,12,Fsaid: "First and foremost, my thoughts
OL,13,Fare with the victim's loved ones as
OL,14,Fthey come to terms with this
OL,15,Fdevastating loss.
OL,26,@tD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
