OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778576786
OL,3,CFamily of father-of-three killed in
OL,4,Cstabbing says his 'legacy will live on'
OL,6,F"This was a brutal attack on our
OL,7,Fstreets which has resulted in a young
OL,8,Fman losing his life. Our officers are
OL,9,Fworking tirelessly to identify all
OL,10,Fthose involved and ensure they are
OL,11,Fbrought to justice without delay.
OL,13,F"The arrests so far reflect the
OL,14,Fextensive work already carried out by
OL,15,Fthe investigation team, and I want to
OL,16,Freassure the public that we will
OL,17,Fcontinue to pursue every line of
OL,18,Fenquiry. No stone will be left
OL,19,Funturned."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
